parameters:
Her name is Vega. She always has a high ranking... She's
very excellent.

Her magic was beautiful. It was refined and had no waste. I
tend to remember things I like one after another, so maybe I
should learn a little from her.

I've been interested for a long time. I've been thinking, if
only we could become friends...
I might be seen as 'arrogant' for saying this, but...

I felt like she was 'viewing me as a rival'. I don't think
she hates me... but I feel like there's an unbridgeable gap.
Hmm... I wonder if there's any way...
